# Daily Habit Tracker Update Walkthrough

## New Features & Changes
### 1. Reset Day Feature 🔄
- **Functionality**: Allows you to reset your daily progress and start fresh.
- **Trigger**: The "Reset Day" button automatically appears on the Dashboard **only when you reach 100% daily goal**.
- **Action**: Clicking it unchecks all habits for the current day.

### 2. Habit Detail UI Update
- **Back Button**: Moved from the top header to the **bottom of the screen**.
- **Design**: Now larger and easier to reach with one hand.

## Build Status
- **Android APK**: Built successfully.
- **Path**: `android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk`

## How to Test
1. **Install APK**:
   - Install the new `app-debug.apk` on your device.

2. **Test Reset Feature**:
   - Check off ALL habits on the dashboard.
   - Verify the "Reset Day 🔄" button appears below the progress bar.
   - Click it and confirm all checkboxes are cleared.

3. **Test Back Button**:
   - Tap on any habit to enter the Detail view.
   - Verify the "Back to Dashboard" button is at the bottom.
   - Click it to return to the dashboard.
